<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/zombie-cells-spark-inflammation-in-severe-fatty-liver-disease-mayo-clinic-researchers-find/">&amp;#8216;Zombie&amp;#8217; cells spark inflammation in severe fatty liver disease, Mayo Clinic researchers find&nbsp;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
