		<title>Get to know your microbiome: It can improve gut health and more, Mayo Clinic expert explains</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/get-to-know-your-microbiome-it-can-improve-gut-health-and-more-mayo-clinic-expert-explains/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Sharon Theimer]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 12 Dec 2025 14:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
